      "raw_text": "Under direction Of Chief En-\ngineer A. NJ. Lupfer, preliminary\nsurveys have been commenced for\nthe subway under Front av. The\ngeneral line runs from the Inland\nEmpire freight yards across Di-\nvision st. between Front av. and\nthe Great Northern bridge, then\nsouth to Front, reaching the latter\nnear Sacred Heart hospital\ngrounds."
